==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Potluck
<hw>Pot"luck`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Whatever may chance
to be in the pot, or may be provided for a meal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A woman whose <qex>potluck</qex> was always to be relied on.</q>
<rj><qau>G. Eliot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To take potluck</b></col>, <cd>to take what food may
chance to be provided.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Potman</ent>⟦br⟧
